page.title: 04ECOLOGY 2
page.content: {FLOWERS (BARNOLDSWICK LN)}primrose, dog- & white- violets, dogs mercury, moschatel , woodsorrel , stitchwort, bluebell, celandine, kingcup, wood anemone, cuckoo flower, cuckoo-pint, daisy, butterburr, bugle, tormentil, knapweed, garlic-mustard, wild garlic, nettle,pink campion, thistle (spear- & field ), meadow buttercup, bush & tufted vetch, bramble, cleavers, hedge parsley , ground ivy , meadowsweet, herb - robert, bird's foot trefoil, valerian, hedge woundwort, dead nettle (red & white),wood avens, oxeye daisy, harebell, yarrow, mugwort, shining - & meadow-cranesbill, comfrey, ivy-leaved toadflax, betony, wall lettuce, honey- suckle, dandelion, silverweed, great burnet, field scabious, lady's mantle, pink & white clover, crosswort, wild strawberry, butcher's broom, hedge - & lady's- bedstraw.
